name: Preach Love
description:
Easily the gang favourite of the first songs we did, epic vibe on the day it was made. Sadly the project was lost before the mix could be finished and so the vocals are kinda quiet in some parts (sorry yall). But it had to make the demo, enjoy it in all its semi-finished majesty: Preach Love, it's all that matters.
BLS, Angel Steamy MC, Jayoscillator
OG Space GOAT 2022.
